#: src/dippi.blp:218
msgid ""
"For LoDPI, a DPI range of <b>90–150 is ideal for desktops</b> while <b>124–156 is ideal "
"for laptops</b>.\n"
"\n"
"For HiDPI, <b>180–300 is ideal for desktops</b> while <b>248–312 is ideal for laptops</b>."
msgstr ""

#: src/dippi.blp:254
msgid "Very Low DPI"
msgstr "ძალიან დაბალი DPI"

#: src/dippi.blp:267
msgid ""
"Text and UI are likely to be too big for typical viewing distances. <b>Avoid if possible."
"</b>"
msgstr ""

#: src/dippi.blp:303
msgid "Fairly Low DPI"
msgstr "საკმაოდ დაბალი DPI"

#: src/dippi.blp:316
msgid ""
"Text and UI might be too big for typical viewing distances, but it's <b>largely up to "
"user preference</b> and physical distance from the display."
msgstr ""

#: src/dippi.blp:352
msgid "Ideal for LoDPI"
msgstr "იდეალურია LoDPI-ისთვის"

#: src/dippi.blp:365
msgid ""
"Not HiDPI, but <b>a nice sweet spot</b>. Text and UI should be legible at typical viewing "
"distances."
msgstr ""

#: src/dippi.blp:401 src/dippi.blp:499 src/dippi.blp:548
msgid "Potentially Problematic"
msgstr "პოტენციურად პრობლემატური"

#: src/dippi.blp:414
msgid ""
"Relatively high resolution, but not quite HiDPI. Text and UI <b>may be too small by "
"default</b>, but forcing HiDPI would make them appear too large. The experience may be "
"slightly improved by increasing the text size."
msgstr ""

#: src/dippi.blp:450
msgid "Tweak for HiDPI"
msgstr "ცვლილებები HiDPI-ისთვის"

#: src/dippi.blp:463
msgid ""
"This display may default to loDPI on some desktops, which could result in too-small text "
"and UI. However, it <b>may be usable with HiDPI by manually enabling 2× scaling</b>. "
"Further adjustments can be made by decreasing the text size."
msgstr ""

#: src/dippi.blp:512
msgid ""
"This display is in a very tricky range and is <b>not likely to work well</b> with integer "
"scaling out of the box."
msgstr ""

#: src/dippi.blp:561
msgid ""
"HiDPI by default, but <b>text and UI may appear too large</b>. Turning off HiDPI and "
"increasing the text size might help."
msgstr ""

#: src/dippi.blp:597
msgid "Ideal for HiDPI"
msgstr "იდეალურია HiDPI-ისთვის"

#: src/dippi.blp:610
msgid ""
"Crisp HiDPI text and UI along with a readable size at typical viewing distances. <b>This "
"is the jackpot.</b>"
msgstr ""

#: src/dippi.blp:646
msgid "Fairly High for HiDPI"
msgstr "საკმაოდ მაღალია HiDPI-ისთვის"

#: src/dippi.blp:659
msgid ""
"Text and UI are likely to appear <b>too small for typical viewing distances</b>. "
"Increasing the text size may help."
msgstr ""

#: src/dippi.blp:708
msgid "Text and UI will appear <b>too small for typical viewing distances</b>."
msgstr ""
